   "note": "旁白"
  },
  {
   "offset": 113,
   "len": 40,
   "en": "\"Thou hast much to learn about honesty.\"",
   "zh": "「汝對誠實仍有許多須學習之處。」",
   "note": "低階評語"
  },
  {
   "offset": 166,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"Thy deeds have shown admirable honesty.\"",
   "zh": "「汝之行為展現了令人欽佩的誠實。」",
   "note": "中階評語"
  },
  {
   "offset": 208,
   "len": 39,
   "en": "\"Thy deeds serve as an example to all.\"",
   "zh": "「汝之行為可為眾人表率。」",
   "note": "高階評語"
  },
  {
   "offset": 251,
   "len": 39,
   "en": "Do you wish to meditate at this altar? ",
   "zh": "你希望在此祭壇冥想嗎？",
