   "note": "聖言，仿聖經腓立比書4:8"
  },
  {
   "offset": 557,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"Whatsoever things are honest...\"",
   "zh": "「凡是誠實之事……」",
   "note": "聖言"
  },
  {
   "offset": 593,
   "len": 75,
   "en": "\"If there be any virtue and if there be any praise, think on these things.\"",
   "zh": "「凡有德行、凡可稱頌者，皆當存念於心。」",
   "note": "聖言"
  },
  {
   "offset": 677,
